citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1110 on
24-JUL-19.
Inspector arrival to premise at 1110 on 24JULY2019. Rang front door bell and knocked. Called primary contact #
and left message. Honked car horn and walked to kennel area, No visible personnel on premises. Left business
card with contact info on door of house. Inspector departure at 1142.
